revision.text: Galar is the eighth region and currently has 108 new Pokémon to catch, breed and hatch. Galar gyms and dungeons are quite tough but offer great rewards as well. At this stage it should be easily possible for the player to give every Pokémon the maximum amount of protein. This region also introduces a new mechanic, The [[Battle Café]].
